    @template ltisource_params/placeholders

    This template provides the layout for list of placeholders avaliable for a given provider.

    Classes required for JS:
    * none

    Data attributes required for JS:
    * none

    Context variables required for this template:
    * mailto

    Example context (json):
    {
        "provider": "Course",
        "placeholders": "Params.course.id, Params.course.name"
    }

}}
<div>
    <h6>{{{provider}}}</h6>
    <p>{{{placeholders}}}</p>
</div>
